Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.04,0:44:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,巨屌爽吗？好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.04,0:45:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.04,0:45:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.04,0:45:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,插的好深
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.08,0:45:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也插插我的啊
