Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.04,0:46:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.08,0:46:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 插的好深
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.04,0:47:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.04,0:47:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,上下的嘴...都插着巨屌
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.08,0:47:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.08,0:47:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,上下都爽？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.04,0:47:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.04,0:47:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.04,0:47:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,又快去了 可以哦 多去几次
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.04,0:48:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
