Dialogue: 0,0:89:54.08,0:89:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 很开心 是很珍贵的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:89:57.08,0:90:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,能听到你这样说很感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:90:00.04,0:90:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大的是怎样的？爽度会改变吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:90:05.04,0:90:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,普通尺寸的 比日本人尺寸大的...
Dialogue: 0,0:90:09.04,0:90:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛 是不太会拘泥大小
Dialogue: 0,0:90:14.04,0:90:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,果然大的话 该说是迫力呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:90:18.04,0:90:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,会插到深处的感觉 很爽
Dialogue: 0,0:90:22.04,0:90:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,SEX的很充实 插着的感觉 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:90:27.08,0:90:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不过太好了 太棒了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:90:31.08,0:90:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是很辛苦的 哪里 彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:90:34.04,0:90:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 是 这拍摄不是很辛苦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:90:39.04,0:90:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,送工作人员 一点小礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:90:43.04,0:90:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有准备了 礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:90:47.04,0:90:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是在那个地方的 能请你戴上眼罩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:90:51.04,0:90:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要是太突然有点那个啊 眼罩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:90:55.04,0:90:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 不好意思 是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:91:00.08,0:91:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那请你敬请期待 好
Dialogue: 0,0:91:03.08,0:91:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那不好意思 牵着手 好
Dialogue: 0,0:91:06.08,0:91:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我来带路 好
Dialogue: 0,0:91:12.04,0:91:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是这边 请
Dialogue: 0,0:91:24.04,0:91:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:91:45.04,0:91:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:92:22.04,0:92:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有好多哦 巨屌
Dialogue: 0,0:92:27.04,0:92:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,都是大的
Dialogue: 0,0:94:10.04,0:94:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真大
Dialogue: 0,0:95:10.04,0:95:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,插进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:95:26.08,0:95:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:95:35.04,0:95:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:95:40.04,0:95:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:95:58.08,0:96:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:96:17.04,0:96:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 又有另一支大肉棒插进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:97:13.04,0:97:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:97:23.04,0:97:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:97:36.04,0:97:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:97:42.08,0:97:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:97:58.04,0:98:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:98:06.04,0:98:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:98:12.08,0:98:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大肉棒好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:98:28.04,0:98:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴快坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:98:51.08,0:98:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,插到深处了
Dialogue: 0,0:99:18.08,0:99:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:99:47.04,0:99:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害...
Dialogue: 0,0:99:52.08,0:99:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽...
Dialogue: 0,0:100:18.04,0:100:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:100:31.08,0:100:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:100:38.04,0:100:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来 是
Dialogue: 0,0:100:55.04,0:100:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:101:01.08,0:101:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,进进出出的
Dialogue: 0,0:101:29.04,0:101:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,又快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:101:34.08,0:101:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:101:51.04,0:101:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:102:01.04,0:102:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:102:04.08,0:102:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:102:24.04,0:102:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那边也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:102:44.08,0:102:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:102:49.04,0:102:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:102:58.04,0:103:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那里不行
Dialogue: 0,0:103:04.04,0:103:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快去了 要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:103:35.04,0:103:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:103:42.04,0:103:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:103:51.08,0:103:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:104:07.04,0:104:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒爽吗？好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:104:13.04,0:104:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:104:29.04,0:104:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:105:03.04,0:105:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:105:08.04,0:105:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:105:28.08,0:105:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:105:33.04,0:105:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:106:23.04,0:106:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:106:53.04,0:106:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,顶到子宫了
Dialogue: 0,0:106:59.04,0:107:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:107:22.04,0:107:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:107:34.04,0:107:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:107:37.08,0:107:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大肉棒爽吗？好爽 真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:107:46.08,0:107:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好大 请再插深点
Dialogue: 0,0:107:58.04,0:108:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:108:18.08,0:108:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 好激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:108:26.04,0:108:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快去了 要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:108:45.08,0:108:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:108:54.04,0:108:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:109:01.04,0:109:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:109:23.08,0:109:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽 快射了
Dialogue: 0,0:109:35.04,0:109:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,又快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:109:42.04,0:109:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:109:57.08,0:110:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:110:03.04,0:110:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,插着好深
Dialogue: 0,0:110:09.04,0:110:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,插到子宫 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:110:16.04,0:110:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:110:25.08,0:110:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...大肉棒 最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:110:36.04,0:110:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我
Dialogue: 0,0:111:02.08,0:111:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还有肉棒哦 给我
Dialogue: 0,0:111:06.08,0:111:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:111:17.04,0:111:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:111:35.08,0:111:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗？真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:111:37.08,0:111:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大肉棒 想要很多
Dialogue: 0,0:111:47.04,0:111:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 里面麻麻的
Dialogue: 0,0:112:04.08,0:112:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:112:15.04,0:112:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,插进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:112:28.04,0:112:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:113:37.04,0:113:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
